39:33.171 --> 39:34.406
- I KNOW.
I KNOW.

39:34.440 --> 39:35.774
- WELL, I WON'T
BE DOING THAT AGAIN.

39:35.807 --> 39:36.942
I MEAN, NOT THAT IT MATTERS,
'CAUSE I DON'T THINK

39:36.975 --> 39:38.610
WE'RE GOING TO BE SPENDING
ANY MORE BIRTHDAYS TOGETHER.

39:38.644 --> 39:39.911
- MY T-CELLS WENT DOWN.

39:39.945 --> 39:42.047
- WHAT?

39:42.080 --> 39:45.651
- AND MY VIRAL LOAD'S
BACK UP.

39:47.786 --> 39:51.490
- HOW UP?
- 125,000.

39:52.724 --> 39:55.727
THAT'S WHERE I WAS
BEFORE I CAME HOME,

39:55.761 --> 39:59.531
AT THE DOCTOR'S,
GETTING THE RESULTS.

39:59.565 --> 40:01.467
THE COCKTAIL'S NOT WORKING.

40:01.500 --> 40:05.737
THE VIRUS HAS BECOME
RESISTANT.

40:05.771 --> 40:07.072
- WELL, CAN'T THEY
CHANGE THE DRUGS?

40:07.105 --> 40:09.407
- THEY ALREADY HAVE.

40:14.079 --> 40:15.514
- SINCE WHEN DO YOU SMOKE?

40:17.816 --> 40:20.018
[shuts lighter]

40:20.051 --> 40:22.621
- SINCE I'M NERVOUS,
MICHAEL.

40:22.654 --> 40:24.823
WOULD YOU STOP
LOOKING AT ME LIKE THAT?

40:24.856 --> 40:27.659
PLEASE.
I'M NOT PERFECT, YOU KNOW?

40:29.928 --> 40:31.096
- YEAH,
I'M FINDING THAT OUT.

40:31.129 --> 40:32.564
- WELL, GOD KNOWS,
I HAVE TRIED.

40:32.598 --> 40:33.999
EASTERN RELIGION,
MEDITATION, YOGA.

40:34.032 --> 40:35.567
YOU NAME IT,
I HAVE PRACTICED IT.

40:35.601 --> 40:38.470
HOPING TO ACHIEVE SOME...
STATE OF INNER HARMONY.

40:38.504 --> 40:41.707
[sighs and chuckles]

40:41.740 --> 40:42.974
AND THEN THIS HAPPENS,
AND I REALIZE

40:43.008 --> 40:45.511
THE ONLY THING
I HAVE ACHIEVED

40:45.544 --> 40:49.047
IS TO CONVINCE MYSELF
I BELIEVE ALL THIS BULLSHIT.

40:49.080 --> 40:52.017
- IT'S NOT BULLSHIT.

40:53.785 --> 40:55.887
- I HURT YOU, MICHAEL.

40:58.524 --> 41:00.692
I HURT THE ONE PERSON

41:00.726 --> 41:03.829
WHO MEANS MORE TO ME
THAN ANYONE ELSE IN THE WORLD,

41:03.862 --> 41:09.134
AND THERE'S NO EXCUSE
FOR IT.

41:09.167 --> 41:12.137
YOU KNOW, THERE'S
JUST NO EXCUSE AT ALL.

41:19.110 --> 41:20.879
- SURE THERE IS.

41:24.816 --> 41:26.952
YOU'RE HUMAN.

42:10.796 --> 42:13.765
[violin playing]

42:13.799 --> 42:21.773
*

42:58.677 --> 43:01.613
[indistinct chatter]

43:10.722 --> 43:13.925
- THOSE ARE NICE.

43:13.959 --> 43:14.960
- MM.

43:16.728 --> 43:18.129
- SHALL I WRAP THEM FOR YOU?

43:28.039 --> 43:30.275
- NO, THANKS.

43:48.727 --> 43:54.165
- * THE LANDSCAPE
OF YOUR HEART UNCHARTED *

43:54.199 --> 43:56.902
* TRAVEL BROCHURES

43:56.935 --> 43:59.137
* TUCKED IN YOUR POCKET

43:59.170 --> 44:02.340
* IN PERFECT DISGUISE

44:02.373 --> 44:07.713
* RIGHT THERE
IN FRONT OF YOU *

44:07.746 --> 44:10.415
* IN PLAIN SIGHT

44:10.448 --> 44:12.984
* YOU MIGHT AS WELL LOOK

44:13.018 --> 44:15.787
* SO CLOSE AT HAND

44:15.821 --> 44:18.857
* BUT YOU MOSTLY FLY OVER

44:18.890 --> 44:21.059
* YOU NEVER LAND

44:21.092 --> 44:24.295
* EVEN A SECOND THOUGHT

44:24.329 --> 44:29.835
* HIDING IN PERFECT DISGUISE

44:29.868 --> 44:32.738
* IN PLAIN SIGHT

44:32.771 --> 44:35.240
* FRIENDS AND RELATIONS

44:35.273 --> 44:37.442
* HAVE TRIED TO SAY

44:37.475 --> 44:40.145
* BUT YOU'LL HAVE NONE OF IT

44:40.178 --> 44:43.114
* BUT THE PROTEST

44:43.148 --> 44:45.350
* OH

44:45.383 --> 44:49.320
* 'CAUSE YOU KNOW

44:49.354 --> 44:54.860
* YOU KNOW BETTER

44:54.893 --> 44:59.731
* THE MOON SNEAKS UP

44:59.765 --> 45:04.302
* ON THE AFTERNOON

45:04.335 --> 45:07.472
* BUT YOU'VE LOOKED DOWN

45:07.505 --> 45:13.078
* SO LONG AT YOUR FEET

45:13.111 --> 45:15.380
*

45:15.413 --> 45:18.817
* AT YOUR FEET

45:18.850 --> 45:21.486
*

45:21.519 --> 45:26.758
* FOR SO LONG

45:26.792 --> 45:32.530
* AT YOUR FEET

45:32.563 --> 45:37.535
* SO LONG

